  "detailed_description": "Country Discoverer is a fast-paced, arcade twin-stick shooter with a high-skill scoring system and robust online leaderboards. Test your reflexes and your intellect as you sail the seas discovering new countries by launching giant telescopes at them as they hurtle towards you. Don't worry about it - it's weird.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388280/extras/450812e7b0434ee53559707e34dcf32c.avif?t=1618585251\" width=616 height=240 /></span><br><br>Your knowledge of our world will be tested as you dodge and dash through a tumultuous sea. Collect powerups, build your multiplier, and go for the ultimate high score!<br><br>Do you have what it takes to become the world's top Country Discoverer?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388280/extras/8d47a079b8c90f6f71070c04a225ca6b.avif?t=1618585251\" width=616 height=240 /></span><br><br>Your ship is waiting, captain.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1388280/extras/70414d12ab46edea128ab0a90d86e271.avif?t=1618585251\" width=616 height=240 /></span><br><br>10% of all profits from Country Discoverer will be donated to the Urban Native Youth Association: ",
